author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Rentabiliweb announces suspension of its shares at request of issuer
text:
Sept 24 Rentabiliweb Group SA :
* Announces the suspension of its shares at the request of the issuer and in agreement with the Belgian financial market and services Authority (FSMA), pending the release of a statement Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
